itchen-cabinet-design-ideas-for-charming-culinary-haven-490x1024.jpg 490w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20174039\/kitchen-cabinet-design-ideas-for-charming-culinary-haven-768x1605.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20174039\/kitchen-cabinet-design-ideas-for-charming-culinary-haven-735x1536.jpg 735w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20174039\/kitchen-cabinet-design-ideas-for-charming-culinary-haven-980x2048.jpg 980w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20174039\/kitchen-cabinet-design-ideas-for-charming-culinary-haven-150x314.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1225px) 100vw, 1225px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Steal The Show With Steel Kitchen Cabinets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know that stainless steel cabinetry for kitchens originally gained popularity because of how affordable and convenient they were to maintain? To think that these glistening beauties were something people would only \u2018make do\u2019 with. See how far they\u2019ve come today. Metal finishes for your cabinets are modern kitchen favourites now because of how sleek and stylish they make your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">kitchen interior<\/a> design to be. Modern interior designs (more often than not) don\u2019t agree with vivid colours and what better way to ditch a bright-coloured palette with glossy silver kitchen cabinets that are simple yet make a sophisticated bold statement at the same time?&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Easy to care for and super budget-friendly \u2013 you can have these shiny surfaces spray painted if you\u2019d like to. But the whole single-toned rustic vibe is something you\u2019re not easily going to want to give up.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/