ng particularly glamorous, our suggestion would be to go with deep dramatic colours in glossy finishes like a cherry\/wine red or a deep royal blue. This could take grandeur in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">modular kitchen<\/a> designs to a whole other level!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Modular kitchen cabinets with glossy finish of drawers in black and white on the top in corner kitchen cabinet\" class=\"wp-image-3913\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235031\/modular-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Alluring glossy black kitchen cabinets in a modern open kitchen is a grand choice<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Kitchen cabinet design to glam up your interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/17142806\/kitchen-cabinet-design-to-glam-up-your-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The (Pastel) Pink Panther For A Soothing Aura<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For simple and elegant kitchen design, you can always choose to spruce up with neutral shades that are soothing to the eye. Milder shades of brown, pink and green appear light and fresh and add a lot of character to your kitchen cabinet designs when compared to other neutrals. The only thing that\u2019s missing now is a couple of plants to bring out the earthiness of pastel shades and you\u2019re good to go!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen Cabinets online with a pastel look of elegant white colour cabinets in ready made kitchen cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-3916\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235035\/kitchen-cabinets-online-in-pastel-style-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Warm pastel brown and white colour kitchen cabinets in open kitchen design are soothing and warm<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Metallic Kitchen Cabinets That Truly Mesmerise<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There\u2019s something about modern metallic interiors that instantly introduces a wave of sophistication and style to your kitchen without having to put in much effort in doing so. If making a statement with your kitchen cabinets is what you\u2019re aiming for, don\u2019t think twice before incorporating metallic gold gushes in between stylish stainless-steel cabinets to dress-up this otherwise mundane room.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Metal kitchen cabinets with golden finish on upper and lower cabinets in curved style of kitchen cabinet doors\" class=\"wp-image-3917\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235040\/metal-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Golden metallic kitchen cabinets in a contemporary kitchen for those who love everything refined<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"The Secret to Trendy Kitchen Cabinets in 2024\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/CrIs1mWQD5U?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Be Innovative With Mixed Materials<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Too confused with too much to choose from? Stir things up a little by pairing textures or materials to make the most of your kitchen space. Blush-toned backsplashes call for a rather nature-inspired look with warm wooden hues and rustic brick fittings. Even otherwise, there\u2019s a lot you can experiment with when it comes to spicing up with textures. Stainless steel works stunningly well with white wooden cabinets and gives your kitchen a very chic and contemporary vibe. A textured play doesn\u2019t even necessarily have to involve a combination of two or more different materials, to be honest. Take the example of wood. There are a million ways you can up your kitchen cabinet game using different textures of wood to give an effervescent elegance.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen cabinet colors with mixed materials of stainless steel and glossy finish in kitchen cabinets pictures gallery\" class=\"wp-image-3922\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235050\/kitchen-cabinet-colors-made-up-of-mixed-materials-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Stainless steel fittings in between white wooden cabinets that complement the hardwood floor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a kitchen that's perfect for your dream home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27172636\/get-kitchen-that-perfect-like-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get Off The Floor With Floating Kitchen Cabinets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Installing floating kitchen cabinets can be a great way to flaunt those hardwood floors and open up space quite effortlessly. Say goodbye to kitchen crumbs that will no longer accumulate with these stylish elevated enchanters. In addition to this, modern floating kitchen cabinets make rightful use of small spaces and happen to be a saving grace for weak backs who find it difficult to bend.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen cabinets with glossy white finish in l-shaped kitchen\" class=\"wp-image-3923\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235056\/modern-kitchen-cabinets-with-glossy-finish-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Polished floating kitchen cabinets with glossy white finishing and backlit backsplashes<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Wooers &#8211; An All-Time Classic<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know that wood is the most common material used for kitchen cabinets? They continue to remain a go-to choice till date because of their timeless charm and customisable properties. Unlike steel, they\u2019re so much easier to maintain and also manage to effortlessly add that classic refined look to your kitchen interior.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Wood Kitchen Cabinets with light finish on the upper cabinets and the drawers as well for small kitchen cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-3924\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235101\/wood-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Textured wooden kitchen cabinets in a modern studio apartment<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Handleless Wooden Kitchen Cabinets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Minimalistic modern kitchen designs ensure that space is a priority. By ditching cabinet handles, you\u2019re not only going to be adding to seamless sophistication in design but also going to be making your kitchen look a lot less cluttered.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen storage cabinets which are handleless and with heavy wooden finish for images of wine cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-3925\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235106\/kitchen-storage-cabinets-for-your-home-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Handleless wooden kitchen cabinets for a seamless and elegant look&nbsp;<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Have you ever seen a smartly designed kitchen\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170153\/smartly-designed-kitchen.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Free The Floor With Kitchen Wall Cabinets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wall ceilings are underrated storage saviours. If a lack of floor space is impeding free movement in and out of your kitchen, always consider wall cabinets to redd up (and rev up) the room. Not only do they free up floor space, but also make the in-between walls available for decorative backsplashes!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen wall cabinet design attached on the wall in cheap kitchen cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-3926\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235110\/kitchen-wall-cabinet-design-for-your-home-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Space-saving wooden cabinets etched on to the ceiling wall of a modern open kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corner Cabinet Designs For A Clutter-Free Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With a lack of space in most apartments today, chances are that you\u2019re struggling to find storage to stuff the many to-use-later items that every Indian kitchen possesses. Using that teeny extra space in every nook and corner to build extra kitchen cabinets can go a long way catering to your extra storage requirements. So go ahead and tighten up those kitchen walls only so you can declutter later.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Corner kitchen cabinet in wooden finish with steel chimney and drawers is ideal for small kitchen\" class=\"wp-image-3927\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235115\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-for-your-home-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Textured wooden kitchen cabinets in the corner wall of a tiny kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/corner-kitchen-cabinet-ideas\/\">Corner Kitchen Cabinet Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Upper Glass Kitchen Cabinets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For a rich and airy feel, complement your all-white kitchen with glass cabinet designs that seem to have a gazillion benefits. Besides the obvious elegance that glassing up space brings, the transparent light reflector also makes a kitchen seem inflated. If you don\u2019t wish to parade your spice jars with these invisible sheets, you can always choose clouded glass designs with pretty prints that add to the beauty of your kitchenette while also concealing all that is within. Win-Win!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"820\" height=\"820\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Glass kitchen cabinets with wooden in white colour and large shutters on the bottom in kitchen glass cabinet designs\" class=\"wp-image-3928\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home.jpg 820w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235120\/glass-kitchen-cabinets-for-your-home-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Glass fittings complimenting the white of kitchen cabinets in a classy kitchen design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you know which modular kitchen is durable & safe\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170613\/which-modular-kitchen-is-durable-and-safe.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kitchen cabinets have come a long way as you might have guessed and are no longer just functional in nature. The choice of design, style, finishes, and colour has become food for thought for homeowners \u2013 literally!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Kitchen Cabinet Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Can I paint my kitchen cabinets a different color than the rest of the kitchen?<\/strong><br>Yes, painting your kitchen cabinets a different color than the rest of the kitchen is a popular and creative design choice. It adds visual interest and creates a contrast that gives your kitchen a unique and personalized look. Keep in mind the size and layout of your kitchen when choosing a cabinet color. Choose a cabinet color that complements or contrasts with the existing color palette in your kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. How do I choose the right hardware for my kitchen cabinets?<\/strong><br>When choosing the right hardware for your kitchen cabinets, think about the style and theme of your kitchen. Are you going for a modern, traditional, rustic, or eclectic look? Choose hardware that complements the overall style. Take into account the finish of your cabinets. Based on this you can opt for matching hardware finish to create a cohesive look or choose hardware that contrasts with the cabinet finish for a more dramatic effect. Make sure the hardware is easy to grip and operate by testing the handles and knobs to ensure comfortable use.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Should I choose custom or pre-made cabinets for my kitchen renovation?<\/strong><br>Choosing between custom or pre-made cabinets for your kitchen renovation depends on various factors, including your budget, timeline, design preferences, and specific needs. Custom cabinets are typically more expensive than pre-made cabinets due to the personalized design and craftsmanship involved. But they allow you to tailor every aspect to your specific requirements, ensuring you get a perfect fit for your kitchen. On the other hand, pre-made cabinets are a more time-efficient option as they do not require design consultations or measurements, unlike custom cabinets.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. What are some popular styles for kitchen cabinet doors?<\/strong><br>Here are some popular styles for kitchen cabinet doors:<br>1) Raised Panel: Raised panel cabinet doors have a raised center panel with a surrounding frame. This classic style adds depth and dimension to the cabinets, ideal for traditional kitchen cabinet door designs.<br>2) Flat Panel: Flat panel cabinet doors have a flat, smooth surface without any raised panels. This minimalist style offers a sleek and contemporary look, ideal for modern and minimalist kitchen designs.<br>3) Glass Front: Glass front cabinet doors feature panels made of glass, which can be clear, frosted, or textured. This style allows you to display your crockery and dishware. Glass front doors give your kitchen an open and airy feel.<br>4) Beaded: Beaded cabinet doors feature vertical grooves or panels reminiscent of traditional beadboard wall paneling. This style adds texture and a charming rustic or farmhouse vibe to your kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. How can I incorporate glass into my kitchen cabinet design?<\/strong><br>To incorporate glass into your kitchen cabinet design, opt for glass shelves inside your cabinets. If you prefer to keep solid cabinet doors but still want to incorporate glass, consider adding glass inserts. These are panels of glass that fit into the cabinet door frames, allowing you to display items while maintaining the overall structure of the cabinet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 